extendedInfo.description: How much of a fan of One Direction are you? This Quiz is free and will test your knowledge of the band. This Quiz has the following: ** Beautiful retina quality graphics ** Questions of ALL of the band members ** Random gameplay no repeating questions in each run ** No need to type anything in questions are all multichoice buttons making easy fun gameplay ** Questions come at random so won't be seeing the same questions every time you play ** HeyZap to compete against your friends *** More questions coming soon *** More features coming soon LegalThis trivia app is unofficial and not affiliated with One Direction in any way. reviews.title: Horrible
reviews.comment: I thought this game was going to be a game of knowledge about the boys. But when you start it it gives you random answers that dont even apply to the question and some ofthe questions dont have the right answer. Im a Directioner and I knew all the answers to the questions asked but the right answer wasnt available. This app needs improvement  -Directioner Pride
